'''威利·韋爾遜'''（{{lang-en|Willie Wilson}}；{{bd|1948年|6月16日|}}<ref>[http://www.thehistorymakers.com/biography/willie-l-wilson-41  BusinessMakers, MusicMakers - Willie L. Wilson] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thehistorymakers.com/biography/willie-l-wilson-41 |date=20170204000450 }} The HistoryMakers. July 16, 2008. Accessed June 4, 2015.</ref>），是美國[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的商人和政治人物，他擁有並經營幾家不同的[[麥當勞|麥當勞]]餐廳，亦持有進口分銷乳膠手套和其他醫療安全用品的奧馬爾醫療用品<ref name="HeadsToIA">[http://chicago.suntimes.com/news/7/71/652695/white-house-sights-willie-wilson-heads-iowa With White House in his sights, Willie Wilson heads to Iowa] {{Wayback|url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/news/7/71/652695/white-house-sights-willie-wilson-heads-iowa |date=20150604011623 }} ''[[Chicago_Sun_Times|Chicago Sun Times]]''. June 1, 2015. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref><ref>[http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/politics/ct-willie-wilson-chicago-mayor-met-0213-20150212-story.html#page=1 Willie Wilson selling up-by-the-bootstraps story in Chicago mayor race] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/local/politics/ct-willie-wilson-chicago-mayor-met-0213-20150212-story.html#page=1 |date=20190222203217 }} Chicago Tribune. February 13, 2015. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref>。他還製作了一個美國[[福音音樂|福音音樂]]電視節目《Singsation》，於2012年獲得[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]<ref name="HeadsToIA"/><ref>[http://www.redeyechicago.com/news/redeye-elections-chicago-mayoral-candidate-willie-wilson-profile-20150211-story.html Meet mayoral candidate Willie Wilson, the anti-politician] {{Wayback|url=http://www.redeyechicago.com/news/redeye-elections-chicago-mayoral-candidate-willie-wilson-profile-20150211-story.html |date=20151024221343 }} ''[[RedEye|RedEye]]''. February 11, 2015. Accessed June 6, 2015.</ref><ref>[http://chicago.suntimes.com/news/7/71/356245/willie-wilson-sharecroppers-son-businessman-chicago-mayor Sharecropper’s son turned successful businessman, Wilson wants ‘equal opportunity for all’] {{Wayback|url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/news/7/71/356245/willie-wilson-sharecroppers-son-businessman-chicago-mayor |date=20150604011417 }} ''Chicago Sun Times''. February 9, 2015. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref>。

==政治生涯==
===競逐芝加哥市長===
韋爾遜參加了{{le|2015年芝加哥市長選舉|Chicago mayoral election, 2015|2015年}}{{le|芝加哥市長|Mayor of Chicago}}的選舉，在五名候選人排名第三，得票率為10.66%<ref>[http://www.chicagoelections.com/en/wdlevel3.asp?elec_code=10 2015 Municipal General - 2/24/15 -- Mayor] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chicagoelections.com/en/wdlevel3.asp?elec_code=10 |date=20160304074043 }} Chicago Board of Elections Commissioners. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref><ref>[http://abc7chicago.com/politics/chicago-businessman-ready-to-challenge-emanuel-in-mayors-race/402910/ Chicago businessman Willie Wilson ready to challenge Emanuel in mayor's race] {{Wayback|url=http://abc7chicago.com/politics/chicago-businessman-ready-to-challenge-emanuel-in-mayors-race/402910/ |date=20150604011515 }} ''[[WLS-TV|WLS-TV]]''. November 19, 2014. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref><ref>[http://wgntv.com/2015/02/18/race-for-chicago-mayor-willie-wilson-says-emanuel-is-an-old-snake-in-new-skin/ Race for Chicago Mayor: Willie Wilson says Emanuel is ‘an old snake in new skin’] {{Wayback|url=http://wgntv.com/2015/02/18/race-for-chicago-mayor-willie-wilson-says-emanuel-is-an-old-snake-in-new-skin/ |date=20190226173140 }} ''[[WGN-TV|WGN-TV]]'' February 18, 2015. June 3, 2015.</ref>。在決選中，他支持初選排名第二的候選人{{le|赫蘇斯·「丘伊」·加西亞|Jesús "Chuy" García}}<ref>[http://chicago.suntimes.com/news/7/71/435489/willie-wilson-even-president-obama-convince-back-rahm Willie Wilson: Not even President Obama could convince me to back Rahm]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}  ''[[Chicago_Sun_Times|Chicago Sun Times]]''. June 1, 2015. Accessed June 3, 2015.</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/13/us/politics/willie-wilson-despite-a-plea-by-obama-gives-a-lift-to-rahm-emanuels-challenger-jesus-garcia.html?_r=0 Key Chicago Figure, Despite a Plea by Obama, Gives a Lift to Emanuel’s Rival] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/13/us/politics/willie-wilson-despite-a-plea-by-obama-gives-a-lift-to-rahm-emanuels-challenger-jesus-garcia.html?_r=0 |date=20191206164929 